A list of customer reviews of three shabu restaurants has been provided.
I utilise it to develop a simple product which will help a business owners to identify their competitive counterparts.
You can imagine such that as a business owner you need to identify competitor(s) in the market.
As you are running business, the market has been developing. Commercial landscape might change and turns to be different from the beginning.
As a result, you want to verify/ benchmark your market position.
